  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know that-- the concert direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under the auspices of the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- after many, many years, I understood actually that this happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because to me, they used to say, no, you never received anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or that this agreement is invalid, and they are not able to allow me to travel to France where my uncle arranged a concerts.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it's very complicated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have what to do in Bulgaria, that I am not allowed because the conservatory is-- supposedly, is not allowing-- grant me a, a time to go to take time off from my teachings.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With one or other words, very soon become clear to me that I am becoming [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] very black stain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My dossier there, in the police, is receiving this kind of status in which the country become one prison for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is when I decided to, to leave the country there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I, I was of Jewish descendance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Secondly, I-- my descendance was from bourgeois descendance, not from proletariat descendance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Thirdly, there was somebody in political circle that wanted to promote somebody else because they sended someone else in my place when I was invited.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, when one person there is gifted, and it's not their-- of their own-- always produced some kind of jealousy and some kind of feelings, negative feelings that, if they have the opportunity, they will eventually show that and will give open green light of one so-called their persons.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not one of-- I'm-- now, when I go out, I'm not representing their country because I don't have the Bulgarian name, which is [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] Edward Polidi, a Jewish person of our country.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this is politically not correct.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
